Creator : Keanu Chetty
Title : Finding Files and Directories
Languages : N/A
Software :Kali Linux

//////////////////////////// Methods to find directories or files /////////////////////////////////
  // Commands //
  // find //
  -> used to find files and directories 
     // Variations //
      -> -iname : searches using the files name and ignores the letter case
      -> -mmin : searches the system looking for files modified x minutes ago 
      -> -user : searches for files created by a specific user
      -> -size : searches for a size of a specified size 
          -> size suffixes 
              -> c : bytes 
              -> k : kilobytes 
              -> M : megabytes 
              -> G : gigabytes
      -> -type : searches for a specific type of file 
  // locate //
  -> locates the file by taking advantage of an index or database
      // Variations //
      -> -i : doesn't consider letter case
      -> -e : This validates that the file or directory actually exists 
        // Need to Know //
          -> updatedb : this will update the database 
  // which //
  -> finds a file with a specific attribute 
  -> gives the absolute path of the linux command
  
